Package: AF3Input
Title: Generate AlphaFold 3 Input JSON for Nucleic Acid Candidates
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R:
    person("Peter", "Huang", email = "peter.huang@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Peter Huang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Peter Huang <peter.huang@example.com>
Description: Utilities to transform tabular nucleic acid candidate calls,
    such as G-quadruplex candidate tables, into AlphaFold 3 input JSON files.
    The package supports configurable sequence columns, metadata descriptions,
    DNA copy number, reverse-complement handling, optional complementary DNA
    strands, DNA base modifications, ions represented as CCD ligands, and model
    seed configuration.
